oracle.pgx.api

Interface PgqlResultSet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.lang.Iterable<PgxResult>, oracle.pgql.lang.ResultAccess, oracle.pgql.lang.ResultSet, oracle.pgql.lang.spatial.STResultAccess

    public interface PgqlResultSet
extends oracle.pgql.lang.ResultSet, oracle.pgql.lang.spatial.STResultAccess, java.lang.Iterable<PgxResult>
    Result set of a pattern matching query. Note: retrieving results from the server is not thread-safe
